  "title": "Fresh Grad - Sales Explorer *ASAP* (B2B, Fun Team, Mentorship Provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 Fresh Grad Sales Explorer – ASAP Start!</strong><br>\n <em>B2B | Fun Team | Mentorship Provided</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Just graduated and not sure where to start? No worries — we’ve got you. Step into the world of B2B sales with full support, great vibes, and endless room to grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re looking for go-getters to join us as <strong>Sales Explorers</strong> — no prior experience needed, just the right attitude!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong><br>\n💼 Connect with businesses to offer solutions that matter<br>\n🎯 Learn how to pitch, close deals, and build long-term customer-client relationships<br>\n📚 Hands-on training and get mentored by experienced leaders.<br>\n🤝 Be part of a supportive team that celebrates every win (big or small!)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Company Perks:</strong><br>\n✅ Full training &amp; 1-on-1 mentorship <br>\n✅ Lively, dynamic team that’s fun to work with<br>\n✅ Clear career path &amp; growth opportunities<br>\n✅ Performance-based incentives <br>\n✅ Fixed hours — fixed schedules!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>You’re a Great Fit If You:</strong><br>\n✨ Just graduated or ORD-ed (welcome!!)<br>\n✨ Love engaging with people and learning new things<br>\n✨ Are driven, curious, and not afraid to try<br>\n✨ Want to start your career in a supportive, exciting environment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Your next chapter starts here — and it’s going to be a fun ride.<br>\n📩 <u>Apply now</u> and let’s explore your future together!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
